{"tid":1594714,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛第一個任務---屌跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T05:19:03.000Z","uid":22855,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"714aca00709404a9bb6eb89e5383333b021b8b7c","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"發現好撚多人話唔好跳閘 容許我逐一屌柒你班反跳閘撚<br />\n<br />\n對我黎講，跳/撞/踢閘目的有兩個<br />\n1. 抵抗港鐵，唔單止係為果幾蚊，更多既係為我既骨氣<br />\n2. 突破和理非心理關口<br />\n<br />\n有人話餵食好有用，所以唔應該冒險跳/撞/踢閘。<br />\n答： <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餵食有用，但你會唔會幫手餵食先？</span></span>  如果你比正價，同時只係口頭上支持其他人餵食 咁係咪講緊：「我支持你地做架架，不過我唔會冒險做囉，你地幫我手抵抗左港鐵啦thanks haha」<br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以雙管齊下？<br />\n我見到有好多便衣同黃衫 咁咪唔跳 用綠卡/比正價<br />\n你係女仔/行動不便/身手唔好 咁咪用綠卡<br />\n你唔想冒任何險 咁咪罷搭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本你話成本太高 然後用番正價 就係比藉口自己唔冒任何風險 最自撚私既成果收割者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第2點，你唔敢做任何既反抗行為，係唔會突破任何心理關口<br />\n由掟蛋到掟磚到掟酒落地（到他朝既掟狗） 所有勇武派都係要不停突破心理關口 一步一步黎 冇人可以一步登天<br />\n依家跳/撞/踢閘/用綠卡  就正正係一個最好既機會比你習慣呢種反抗既心態，邊個勇武唔係由和理非開始？<br />\n你可以有心理關口 大家都有 但你必須要做既 係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嘗試</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：日日踢，眼見10個站 得0.1個係重兵  得3-4 個係得一條友鳩hea hea 咁望 連check飛部機都冇拎係手"},{"pid":"3b2e10164319f13c4fd0cd3dcfb7db9f55441c07","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"明顯3毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOmnmAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOmnmAM.png&h=d3cbc549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到日日撚都勁比比人捉 仲要打殘體<br />\n可能唔係三毛 應該係弱智"},{"pid":"8d2f54175541769bec5b06ee457fdf323f7b7080","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"9d971dc75328eb2e297bd3fc63043ef0f0380700","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"73f28be0ef7fdf27ea30182fb1d3153603938ffa","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"9fbabaeb2e836a4edf0ff9af9110cabce1aa46b8","tid":1594714,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"［香港獨立！唯一岀路！］<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警世】不要再執迷於追求五大訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594691</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWKL3KV.jpg&h=63206eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGKzOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGKzOZ.jpg&h=bcba39e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqWCakp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqWCakp.jpg&h=6804524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFLjcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFLjcd.jpg&h=70135473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f2e3527bdf6162aee35c8af0d9a990a1d0c4745","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"ce2bb0bc14971ea1ab2fd34a6e133ed42ee884bc","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"914e68aca22e3ed629a6cd767835ffc0256b31dc","tid":1594714,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"推 6/10"},{"pid":"3a8e3fb61ed62c64f9d1da96cfb31b449e4527a2","tid":1594714,"uid":308682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re